<![CDATA[<p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">{!Contact.FirstName},</p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">On behalf of Borrego Solar, I want to welcome you to the <i><b>VIP Experience</b></i>!&nbsp; You are among a select few clients chosen to be part of this new initiative for 2013 intended to enhance your overall customer experience.&nbsp;<span style="font-size: 11pt;">As Borrego Solar's newly appointed Customer Experience Manager, I'll be introducing you to a VIP program developed to reward you for your business and continued support.</span></p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">What is included within the VIP Experience?</p><ul type="disc" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0.375in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in;"><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: middle;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;">An <b>Online Customer Portal</b> featuring a comprehensive portfolio of product information, real-time system updates and the ability to report a problem to our Operations &amp; Maintenance department at any time, day or night</span></li></ul><ul type="disc" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0.375in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in;"><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: middle;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;">A <b>Customer Appreciation Program</b> including social events, giveaways and a robust referral program that rewards you for acting as a reference and referring new customers</span></li></ul><ul type="disc" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0.375in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in;"><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: middle;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;"><b>Advanced Monitoring</b> of your solar installation's output and delivery of detailed system performance reports</span></li></ul><ul type="disc" style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 0.375in; direction: ltr; unicode-bidi: embed; margin-top: 0in; margin-bottom: 0in;"><li style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; vertical-align: middle;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt;">Free <b>Community Education Sessions</b> for the audience of your choice focused on renewable energy and the positive impact of your solar installation</span></li></ul><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">The <b><i>VIP Experience</i></b> is our way of saying "Thank You" for being one of our most valued customers.</p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">I'll be in touch in the coming weeks &nbsp;to introduce myself and get you set up on the Customer Portal. If you have any questions in the meantime, please don't hesitate to reach out to me directly.</p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">&nbsp;</p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">Happy New Year and I look forward to connecting with you soon,</p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;"><br></p><p style="font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;">Tommy Sunderland</p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;"><br></p><p style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Calibri; font-size: 11pt; margin: 0in;"><p style="margin: 0in; font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;